            "detailed_description": "Hello, and welcome to Spheroid Classic!​<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSpheroid Classic is an early version of Spheroid, A 2.5d Platforming game currently under development.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn Spheroid Classic, you are in control of a robotic blue ceramic sphere equipped with a taser-like electrical feild which is used to activate various gameplay mechanics, which vary across 3 wildly different worlds.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWith each world, you may unlock new Spheroid Skins to play as, and there is also a &quot;Cheats&quot; menu which allows a very small ahndful of codes to be input, namely &quot;lockpick&quot; and &quot;tiny&quot;.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWith any Early-access purchase of Spheroid Classic, You will receive access to the Full-overhaul release of the game when it is nearly complete, simply entitled &quot;Spheroid&quot;, and this version will be moved to a public beta branch at that time.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n(one of the worlds has copyrighted music- I apoligize, Wintergatan. I will not be using the song in the final game. Please contact me again if you need me to patch this version of the game to remove the song.)",
            "about_the_game": "Hello, and welcome to Spheroid Classic!​<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSpheroid Classic is an early version of Spheroid, A 2.5d Platforming game currently under development.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn Spheroid Classic, you are in control of a robotic blue ceramic sphere equipped with a taser-like electrical feild which is used to activate various gameplay mechanics, which vary across 3 wildly different worlds.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWith each world, you may unlock new Spheroid Skins to play as, and there is also a &quot;Cheats&quot; menu which allows a very small ahndful of codes to be input, namely &quot;lockpick&quot; and &quot;tiny&quot;.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWith any Early-access purchase of Spheroid Classic, You will receive access to the Full-overhaul release of the game when it is nearly complete, simply entitled &quot;Spheroid&quot;, and this version will be moved to a public beta branch at that time.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n(one of the worlds has copyrighted music- I apoligize, Wintergatan. I will not be using the song in the final game. Please contact me again if you need me to patch this version of the game to remove the song.)",
